name: com.android.settings.password.SetupChooseLockPassword
description: Setup Wizard's version of ChooseLockPassword screen. It inherits the logic and basic structure from ChooseLockPassword class, and should remain similar to that behaviorally. This class should only overload base methods for minor theme and behavior differences specific to Setup Wizard. Other changes should be done to ChooseLockPassword class instead and let this class inherit those changes.
